default&#xa0;default3.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn 2011, Italy became the first country in the EU to introduce a law prohibiting the distribution of single use plastic bags. Since being passed in March 2012, the law has seen a r
defaulteduc
defaulttion in the
default 
defaultconsumption of plastic bags, and the associated 
defaultenvironm
defaulten
defaulttal impact
defaults. And, led by 
defaultindustrial and societal symbiosis
