defaultVersalis
default and Novamont in Porto Torres in Sardinia. The Porto Torres petrochemical facility is one of Italy’s most important industrial chemical facilities but due to the decline in the overall industry it has in recent years been in crisis. The new joint venture – 
defaultMatrica
default - will see investments of €500M to convert part of the facility into the world’s first third generation 
defaultbiorefinery
